Interface Rfc4515Listener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rfc4515BaseListener

    public interface Rfc4515Listener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by Rfc4515Parser.
